column5: I have not used fish attractants on my many fishing trips to Canada, but I read with interest about a West Coast? company that sells a huge number of attractants. What is your evaluation Pro-Cure products for Walleye and Lakers.? Gunder
really like the walleye trophy sauce and the procure predator is my favorite for icefishing walleyes manitoba .... a 100,000 lakes how many walleyes ???? i will never have enough time....
